OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781628468
OL,3,CPharmacists and taxi drivers help
OL,4,Cpolice crack down on fraud in Cumbria
OL,6,FCumbria Police officers have enlisted
OL,7,Fthe help of pharmacists, taxi drivers
OL,8,Fand businesses to help them warn the
OL,9,Fpublic about fraudsters targeting
OL,10,Fvictims by phone.
OL,12,FThe force is cracking down on
OL,13,Fcriminals who use landlines to con
OL,14,Fpeople out of cash, a practice it
OL,15,Fdescribes as "heartless, cold and
OL,16,Fruthless".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
