FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781628468
OL,3,CPharmacists and taxi drivers help
OL,4,Cpolice crack down on fraud in Cumbria
OL,6,FPCSOs have been going to taxi ranks to
OL,7,Fdistribute literature to the drivers,
OL,8,Fhelping them engage their customers in
OL,9,Fconversation about the issue, while
OL,10,Fchemists have helped raise awareness
OL,11,Fby placing fraud alert cards on their
OL,12,Fcounters.
OL,14,FIn a crime known as courier fraud
OL,15,Fpeople, often vulnerable or elderly,
OL,16,Fare targeted by criminals who pretend
OL,17,Fto be officials.
OL,19,FThey may know a little bit of
OL,20,Finformation about the victim, such as
OL,21,Ftheir name, date of birth or bank.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781628468
OL,3,CPharmacists and taxi drivers help
OL,4,Cpolice crack down on fraud in Cumbria
OL,6,FUsing this information, the fraudsters
OL,7,Fthen ask further questions to build up
OL,8,Ftheir knowledge about the victim, and
OL,9,Fthen make requests for money to be
OL,10,Ftransferred electronically or
OL,11,Fwithdrawn in cash.
OL,13,FCumbria Police says these fraudsters
OL,14,Fcreate a sense of panic to force the
OL,15,Fvictim into acting quickly and
OL,16,Finstinctively, without thinking
OL,17,Flogically.
OL,19,FLast year in Cumbria, victims lost
OL,20,Fover #1,300 to this type of fraud.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781628468
OL,3,CPharmacists and taxi drivers help
OL,4,Cpolice crack down on fraud in Cumbria
OL,6,FCumbria Police says, however, that the
OL,7,Feffect of this type of crime can be
OL,8,Fmore than just financial - with
OL,9,Fvictims often subsequently losing
OL,10,Ftrust in anyone who may try to contact
OL,11,Fthem.
OL,13,FAs such, the constabulary has enlisted
OL,14,Fthe help of people who might regularly
OL,15,Fdeal with older people to raise
OL,16,Fawareness of the crime, such as
OL,17,Fpharmacists and taxi drivers.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781628468
OL,3,CPharmacists and taxi drivers help
OL,4,Cpolice crack down on fraud in Cumbria
OL,6,FFran Henderson, a Cumbria Police
OL,7,Fspecialist in preventing fraud, said:
OL,8,F"The fraudsters who carry out these
OL,9,Foffences are heartless, cold, and
OL,10,Fruthless.
OL,12,F"They target some of the most
OL,13,Fvulnerable in our society. They are
OL,14,Falso very friendly, persuasive, and
OL,15,Fpersistent. They sound completely
OL,16,Fbelievable.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781628468
OL,3,CPharmacists and taxi drivers help
OL,4,Cpolice crack down on fraud in Cumbria
OL,6,F"Their interactions are carefully
OL,7,Fscripted to ensure that the victim is
OL,8,Fconvinced they are either a senior
OL,9,Fpolice officer or a member of an
OL,10,Finternal investigation team within
OL,11,Ftheir bank.
OL,13,F"Under the guise of assisting police
OL,14,For the bank with an investigation,
OL,15,Fvictims are often persuaded to
OL,16,Fpurchase jewellery or gold bullion and
OL,17,Fhand over these high value goods to
OL,18,Fsomeone on their doorstep.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781628468
OL,3,CPharmacists and taxi drivers help
OL,4,Cpolice crack down on fraud in Cumbria
OL,6,F"We need your help to speak to older
OL,7,Ffriends and relatives to explain that
OL,8,Fthey should be cautious when dealing
OL,9,Fwith strangers on the phone, even if
OL,10,Fthey do claim to have an official job
OL,11,Ftitle."
OL,13,FTo further hammer home the message,
OL,14,FPCSOs will engage with doctors'
OL,15,Fsurgeries, opticians, jewellers,
OL,16,Fbureaux de change outlets and gold
OL,17,Fmerchants to help them spot the signs,
OL,18,Fgive warnings and alert police.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,325,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1781628468
OL,3,CPharmacists and taxi drivers help
OL,4,Cpolice crack down on fraud in Cumbria
OL,6,FCumbria's Police, Fire and Crime
OL,7,FCommissioner, David Allen, said:
OL,8,F"These criminals target the most
OL,9,Fvulnerable in our communities so it's
OL,10,Freally important that we look out for
OL,11,Fone another.
OL,13,F"If you have a gut feeling that
OL,14,Fsomething is suspicious or wrong, it
OL,15,Fusually is, so please hang up on the
OL,16,Fperson you are speaking to and report
OL,17,Fit to the police or call the
OL,18,Forganisation the caller says they are
OL,19,Ffrom, such as your bank, to confirm
OL,20,Ftheir identity ` it's better to be
OL,21,Fsafe than sorry."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
